#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gametype:"
msgstr "Vrsta igre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arcade"
msgstr "Arkadna"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiplayer"
msgstr "Igra za več igralcev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&granatier; is a clone of the classic &nbsp;"
"<trademark><application>Bomberman</application></trademark> game, inspired "
"by the work of the <application>Clanbomber</application> clone."
msgstr ""
"&granatier; je klon klasične igre &nbsp;<trademark><application>Bomberman</"
"application></trademark>, ki jo je navdihnilo delo klona "
"<application>Clanbomber</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The object of the game is to run through an arena, using bombs to clear out "
"blocks and eliminate your opponents. Several bonuses and handicaps are "
"hidden underneath the blocks &ndash; these can either help or hinder your "
"progress."
msgstr ""
"Cilj igre je preteči skozi areno z uporabo bomb za odstranjevanje blokov in "
"odstranjevanje nasprotnikov. Pod bloki je skritih več bonusov in ovir "
"&ndash; vam lahko pomagajo ali pa ovirajo vaš napredek."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A &granatier; screenshot</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&granatier; posnetek zaslona</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A &granatier; screenshot</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&granatier; posnetek zaslona</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eliminate all Opponents."
msgstr "Odstraniti vse nasprotnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each player is provided with five keys that they use to move their character "
"and lay bombs. For example, the default keys for Player 1 are the &Up;, "
"&Down;, &Left; and &Right; arrow keys to move respectively in those "
"directions, and the &Enter; key to lay a bomb. Please refer to the <link "
"linkend=\"config_player\">Player Configuration</link> Section to find "
"shortcut keys for other players, as well as how to configure them."
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec ima pet tipk, ki jih uporablja za premikanje svojega lika in "
"polaganje bomb. Na primer, privzete tipke za igralca 1 so &Up;, &Down;, "
"&Left; and &Right; puščične tipke za premikanje v teh smereh in &Enter; "
"tipka za postavitev bombe. Glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"config_player"
"\">Konfiguracija predvajalnika</link>, če želite poiskati tipke za bližnjice "
"za druge igralce in kako jih konfigurirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of laying bombs, aside from attacking other opponents, is to "
"destroy the many blocks scattered throughout the arena in order to clear a "
"path or uncover hidden bonuses. Among the many bonuses that can be uncovered "
"are those that make you move faster or increase your bomb blast range; the "
"more bonuses of this type you collect, the easier it is to eliminate your "
"opponents and win the round. But be warned that just as many handicaps exist "
"that can turn the tide against you, including those that slow you down or "
"invert your moving keys."
msgstr ""
"Namen polaganja bomb, je poleg napada na druge nasprotnike, še uničenje "
"številnih blokov, raztresenih po areni, da bi očistili pot ali odkrili "
"skrite bonuse. Med številnimi bonusi, ki jih je mogoče odkriti, so tisti, "
"zaradi katerih se premikate hitreje ali povečate doseg bombe; več bonusov te "
"vrste zberete, lažje boste odpravili svoje nasprotnike in zmagali v krogu. "
"Vendar bodite opozorjeni, da obstaja prav toliko ovir, ki lahko obrnejo tok "
"proti vam, vključno s tistimi, ki vas upočasnijo ali obrnejo tipke za "
"premikanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each won round, the player is awarded a point. The first player to win a "
"predefined number of points (the default is 3), wins the game!"
msgstr ""
"Za vsako dobljeno rundo igralec prejme točko. Prvi igralec, ki osvoji "
"vnaprej določeno število točk (privzeto je 3), zmaga v igri!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Items"
msgstr "Predmeti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Arena"
msgstr "Arena"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "The players are in an arena which consists of:"
msgstr "Igralci so v areni, ki jo sestavljajo:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Wall"
msgstr "Zid arene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Wall &ndash; this defines the outline of the arena map and cannot be "
"destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Zid &ndash; to določa zunanjo mejo načrta arene in ga ni mogoče uničiti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Ground"
msgstr "Tla arene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Ground &ndash; this can be walked on safely."
msgstr "Tla &ndash; po tleh se da varno hoditi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Ice"
msgstr "Led arene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Ice &ndash; this will make the ground slippery. The speed increases on "
"the ice and it is not possible to completly stop moving."
msgstr ""
"Led &ndash; zaradi tega bodo tla spolzka. Hitrost se na ledu poveča in ni se "
"mogoče popolnoma ustaviti."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Block"
msgstr "Blok arene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Block &ndash; this can be destroyed with a bomb, and may contain a bonus "
"(or a handicap)."
msgstr ""
"Blok &ndash; to je mogoče uničiti z bombo in lahko vsebuje bonus (ali "
"hendikep)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Bomb Mortar"
msgstr "Minomet Arene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Bomb Mortar &ndash; this will throw bombs that are placed on it to "
"random places."
msgstr ""
"Minomet &ndash; to bo vrgel bombe, ki so postavljene nanj, na naključna "
"mesta."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Arrow Right"
msgstr "Arena puščica desno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Arrows &ndash; this will move the bombs that are placed on it to the "
"direction they point."
msgstr ""
"Puščice &ndash; bodo premaknile bombe, ki so na njej, v smer kamor kažejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is none of the above items, there is a hole at the ground and "
"moving into it will result in falling into the deep and die. The same "
"applies also if there is no wall at the edge of the arena and the player "
"moves outside of the arena."
msgstr ""
"Če ni nobenega od zgornjih elementov, je na tleh luknja in če se pomaknete "
"vanjo, boste padli v globino in umrli. Enako velja tudi, če na robu arene ni "
"zidu in se igralec premakne izven arene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bonuses"
msgstr "Bonusi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bonuses are helpful for reaching the game goal and effects exists permanent "
"- even after a handicap disappears. Currently there are following bonuses:"
msgstr ""
"Bonusi so v pomoč pri doseganju ciljev igre in učinki so trajni - tudi "
"potem, ko hendikep izgine. Trenutno obstajajo naslednji bonusi:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Speed"
msgstr "Dodatna hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed &ndash; increases your speed slightly."
msgstr "Hitrost &ndash; nekoliko poveča vašo hitrost."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Bomb"
msgstr "Bonus bomba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bomb &ndash; adds an extra bomb to your arsenal, allowing you to lay more "
"than one bomb at a time."
msgstr ""
"Bomba &ndash; doda dodatno bombo v vaš arzenal, kar vam omogoča, da položite "
"več kot eno bombo hkrati."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Power"
msgstr "Dodatna moč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power &ndash; increases the power of your bombs, extending their bomb blast "
"range."
msgstr "Moč &ndash; poveča moč vaših bomb, s čimer razširi njihov doseg bombe."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Shield"
msgstr "Bonus ščit"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shield &ndash; makes invincible for one bomb blast."
msgstr "Ščit &ndash; vas naredi nepremagljivega za eno eksplozijo bombe."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Throw"
msgstr "Dodatni met"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Throw &ndash; adds the ability to throw bombs. Just press the key for laying "
"bombs while a bomb is below you."
msgstr ""
"Met &ndash; doda možnost metanja bomb. Samo pritisnite tipko za polaganje "
"bomb, medtem ko je bomba pod vami."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Kick"
msgstr "Bonus udarec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kick &ndash; adds the ability to move bombs. Just run against an bomb and "
"the bomb will move."
msgstr ""
"Udarec &ndash; doda možnost premikanja bomb. Samo tecite proti bombi in "
"bomba se bo premaknila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Handicaps"
msgstr "Hendikepi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Handicaps are the opposite of bonuses and hinder the player. The good thing "
"is that effects get lost after some time (other than bonuses) and the player "
"can play in is usual behavior (including bonuses) again. Currently there are "
"following handicaps:"
msgstr ""
"Hendikepi so nasprotje bonusov in ovirajo igralca. Dobra stvar je, da se "
"učinki čez nekaj časa izgubijo (razen bonusov) in igralec lahko spet igra v "
"običajnem vedenju (vključno z bonusi). Trenutno obstajajo naslednji "
"hendikepi:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Slow"
msgstr "Hendikep počasen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slow &ndash; makes you move very slowly."
msgstr "Počasen &ndash; zaradi česar se premikate zelo počasi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Hyperactive"
msgstr "Hendikep hiperaktiven"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hyperactive &ndash; makes you move a little TOO fast."
msgstr "Hiperaktiven &ndash; zaradi česar se premikate PREHITRO."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Mirror"
msgstr "Hendikep ogledala"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mirror &ndash; inverts your moving keys, so that up becomes down and left "
"becomes right."
msgstr ""
"Ogledalo &ndash; obrne vaše tipke premikanja, tako da gor postane dol in "
"levo postane desno."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Scatty"
msgstr "Hendikep bojazljivosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scatty &ndash; forces you to continuously lay bombs without control."
msgstr ""
"Bojazljivost &ndash; vas prisili, da nenehno polagate bombe brez nadzora."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Restrain"
msgstr "Hendikep omejevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restrain &ndash; prevents you to lay bombs."
msgstr "Omejevanje &ndash; preprečuje polaganje bomb."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "The ambivalent Items"
msgstr "Ambivalentni predmeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This type of bonuses are neither good nor bad, it mostly depends on the "
"environment. Currently there are following neutral bonuses:"
msgstr ""
"Tovrstni bonusi niso niti dobri niti slabi, večinoma so odvisni od okolja. "
"Trenutno obstajajo naslednji nevtralni bonusi:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Neutral Pandora"
msgstr "Bonus nevtralna Pandora"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pandora &ndash; this contains either a bonus or a handicap."
msgstr "Pandora &ndash; to lahko vsebuje ali bonus ali hendikep."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Neutral Resurrect"
msgstr "Bonus nevtralni vstanek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resurrect &ndash; this will resurrect any dead player."
msgstr "Vstanek &ndash; to bo obudil vsakega mrtvega igralca."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface Overview"
msgstr "Pregled vmesnika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Items"
msgstr "Elementi menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Starts</action> a new game."
msgstr "<action>Začne</action> novo igro."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &granatier;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &granatier;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvoke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle whether sounds should be played.</action> The default is on."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preklopite, če naj se zvoki predvajajo.</action> Privzeto je "
"vklopljeno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &granatier; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &granatier; ima skupno &kde; <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"elemente menija <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite "
"razdelke o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">meniju z nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the Configuration Dialogue, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &granatier;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo, izberite element menija "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&granatier;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the points which are needed to win the game and the time for "
"a round. After the time is over, the sudden death mode will start."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite lahko točke, ki so potrebne za zmago v igri, in čas za krog. Ko "
"se čas izteče, se bo začel način nenadne smrti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally you can adjust the initial speed, bomb range and bomb armory."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko prilagodite začetno hitrost, doseg bombe in oklep bombe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:297 index.docbook:314 index.docbook:334 index.docbook:348
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A &granatier; Config screenshot</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>A &granatier; Posnetek zaslona konfiguracije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:303 index.docbook:320 index.docbook:340 index.docbook:354
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A &granatier; Config screenshot</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&granatier; Posnetek zaslona konfiguracije</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theme"
msgstr "Tema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select the Theme you want to play, go to the Theme section. The Theme is "
"loaded by clicking on &nbsp;<guibutton>OK</guibutton> or <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>. The current game will be ended and a new one started. You can "
"click on the &nbsp;<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button to restore the "
"default Theme."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati temo, ki jo želite predvajati, pojdite v razdelek Tema. "
"Tema se naloži s klikom na &nbsp;<guibutton>V redu</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>. Trenutna igra se bo končala in začela se bo "
"nova. Lahko kliknete gumb &nbsp;<guibutton>Privzete nastavitve</guibutton>, "
"da obnovite privzeto temo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena"
msgstr "Arena"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select the Arena you want to play, go to the Arena section. The Arena is "
"loaded by clicking on &nbsp;<guibutton>OK</guibutton> or <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>. The current game will be ended and a new one started. You can "
"click on the &nbsp;<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button to restore the "
"default Arena."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati areno, v kateri želite igrati, pojdite v razdelek Arena. "
"Arena se naloži s klikom na &nbsp;<guibutton>V redu</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Uveljavi</guibutton>. Trenutna igra se bo končala in začela se bo "
"nova. Lahko kliknete gumb &nbsp;<guibutton>Privzete nastavitve</guibutton>, "
"da obnovite privzeto areno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have self-made <application>Clanbomber</application> arenas, you can "
"copy them to <filename class=\"directory\">~/.clanbomber/maps</filename>, "
"where &granatier; will look for them. The default <application>Clanbomber</"
"application> arenas are already shipped with &granatier;."
msgstr ""
"Če imate sami izdelane arene <application>Clanbomber</application>, jih "
"lahko kopirate v <filename class=\"directory\">~/.clanbomber/maps</"
"filename>, kjer jih bo &granatier; iskal. Privzete arene "
"<application>Clanbomber</application> so že priložene &granatier;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guibutton>Random Mode</guibutton>, a random arena will be "
"used for each new round. If there are arenas you don't want to play, you can "
"uncheck them."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete <guibutton>Naključni način</guibutton>, bo za vsako novo rundo "
"uporabljena naključna arena. Če obstajajo arene, v katerih ne želite igrati, "
"jih lahko počistite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Player"
msgstr "Igralec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select the Player you want to play, go to the Player section and select "
"the Players with the checkboxes. The Shortcuts can be changed by clicking on "
"the button for the action you want to change and then pressing the key you "
"want to use. The changes are loaded by clicking on &nbsp;<guibutton>OK</"
"guibutton> or <guibutton>Apply</guibutton>. The current game will be ended "
"and a new one started. You can click on the &nbsp;<guibutton>Defaults</"
"guibutton> button to restore the default Shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati igralca, ki ga želite igrati, pojdite v razdelek Igralec "
"in izberite Igralci s potrditvenimi polji. Bližnjice lahko spremenite tako, "
"da kliknete gumb za dejanje, ki ga želite spremeniti, in nato pritisnete "
"tipko, ki jo želite uporabiti. Spremembe se naložijo s klikom na &nbsp;"
"<guibutton>V redu</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Uveljavi</guibutton>. Trenutna "
"igra se bo končala in začela se bo nova. Lahko kliknete gumb &nbsp;"
"<guibutton>Privzete nastavitve</guibutton>, da obnovite privzete bližnjice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a custom Arena"
msgstr "Ustvarite areno po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An Arena in &granatier; consists of two files, the <filename>myarena."
"desktop</filename>&nbsp; and the <filename>myarena.xml</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Arena v &granatier;ju je sestavljena iz dveh datotek, <filename>myarena."
"desktop</filename>&nbsp; in <filename>myarena.xml</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> file contains the "
"metadata like the arena name or the author of the arena and consists of the "
"following entries."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> vsebuje metapodatke, "
"kot je ime arene ali avtor arene, in je sestavljena iz naslednjih vnosov."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[Arena]\n"
"Name=My Arena\n"
"Description=This is my first Arena\n"
"Type=XML\n"
"FileName=myarena.xml\n"
"Author=Joe User\n"
"AuthorEmail=joe.user@foo.org"
msgstr ""
"[Arena]\n"
"Name=My Arena\n"
"Description=This is my first Arena\n"
"Type=XML\n"
"FileName=myarena.xml\n"
"Author=Joe User\n"
"AuthorEmail=joe.user@foo.org"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whatever name you want, but &nbsp;<literal>FileName</literal> "
"must be the name of the <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal> file."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko poljubno ime, vendar &nbsp;<literal>ImeDatoteke</literal> "
"mora biti ime datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal> file contains the actual "
"arena map."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka <literal role=\"extension\">.xml</literal> vsebuje dejanski načrt "
"arene."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;\n"
"&lt;Arena arenaFileVersion=\"1\" rowCount=\"13\" colCount=\"17\"&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;    ==== ====    &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  ===+++++++===  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  =+++++_+++++=  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; ==+++=_p_=+++== &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;==++===_-_===++==&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;=+++=++_-_++=+++=&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; +++++-- --+++++ &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;=+++=++_-_++=+++=&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;==++===_-_===++==&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; ==+++=_p_=+++== &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  =+++++_+++++=  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  ===+++++++===  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;    ==== ====    &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"&lt;/Arena&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\"?&gt;\n"
"&lt;Arena arenaFileVersion=\"1\" rowCount=\"13\" colCount=\"17\"&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;    ==== ====    &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  ===+++++++===  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  =+++++_+++++=  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; ==+++=_p_=+++== &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;==++===_-_===++==&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;=+++=++_-_++=+++=&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; +++++-- --+++++ &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;=+++=++_-_++=+++=&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;==++===_-_===++==&lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt; ==+++=_p_=+++== &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  =+++++_+++++=  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;  ===+++++++===  &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"  &lt;Row&gt;    ==== ====    &lt;/Row&gt;\n"
"&lt;/Arena&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is no limit for <literal>rowCount</literal> and <literal>colCount</"
"literal>, so you can choose the size of the arena by yourself. The following "
"symbols are used for the arena map."
msgstr ""
"Za <literal>rowCount</literal> in <literal>colCount</literal> ni omejitev, "
"tako da lahko sami izberete velikost arene. Za načrt arene se uporabljajo "
"naslednji simboli."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"'=' a wall item\n"
"' ' a hole item\n"
"'_' a ground item\n"
"'+' a block item\n"
"'x' will randomly create a block or a ground item\n"
"'-' an ice item\n"
"'o' a mortar item\n"
"'u' an arrow up\n"
"'r' an arrow right\n"
"'d' an arrow down\n"
"'l' an arrow left\n"
"'p' a player position"
msgstr ""
"'=' zidni element\n"
"' ' luknja\n"
"'_' element na tleh\n"
"'+' blok\n"
"'x' bo naključno ustvaril blok ali element na tleh\n"
"'-' led\n"
"'o' minomet\n"
"'u' puščica gor\n"
"'r' puščica desno\n"
"'d' puščica dol\n"
"'l' puščica levo\n"
"'p' mesto igralca"

